    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us man:\nRas eſſi tu? Es fazziju us to: Es\neſſinu weens Amalekitereis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us man:\nNahz tchur pee manni/ un noꞥau-\nji man/ jo Isbailes irr mann aie-\nnehmuſchas/ un manna Dsihwi-\nba irr wehl weffela eeſsch mannis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad peegabju es pee ta/\nun nokawu to/ jo es gan finnajn\nka wiꞥſch pehz tawas Kriſchanas\nne warreja dsihwoht/ un es xeh-\nmu to Krohni/ kas us winna\nGalwu bija/ un winna Rohku-\nGreschunnu/ un eſſnu to pee\nmannu Kungu ſchurp neſſis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fakampe Dahwids us taweem Angstuineem ir\nfawas Drehees/ un faplohfija winsch nokauts! ka irr tee Wa-\ntahs/ ta patt arri wiſſi tee Wihr-\nri/ kas pee winna bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee ſchehlojahs/ un ran-\ndaja/ un gaueja lihds Wakkaram\npahr Saulu/ un pahr winna\nDehlu Jonatanu/ un pahr wiſ-\nfeem Landim ta KUNGA/ un\npahr Israëta Naïnu/ tapehz ka\ntee zaur Sohbinu bij krittuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fazzija us\nto Puifi/ kas winnam to hijstah-\nfijs : No kurrenes tu eſſi? un\nwiꞥſch fazzija : Es eſſinu weena\nfwefcha Mihras/ weena Amaleki-\ntera Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fazzija us\nto: Ka/ ne eſſi tu bihjajees tawu\nRohku isstept ta KUNGA\nSwaiditu nomaitaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Unj Dahwids aizinaja\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fazzija u\nto: Taws Affins laid paleek u\ntawu Galwu/ jo tawa Mutt\nirr prett tew paſchu runnajfs/ ta-\nzidama: Es eſſinu ta KUNG\nSwaiditu nokawis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſchehlojahsDahwids a\nfcho Schehlochannu pahr Saulu\nun pahr winna Dehlu Jonatanu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pawehleja/ ka toh\nBehrnus no Judha bij to Stoh\npu mahziht: Redſi/ tas irr ra-\nſtihts eeſsch tahs Grahmatas t\nTaijna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ak Israëta Glihtums\nus taweem Angstuineem ir\nwinsch nokauts! ka irr tee Wa-\nrenee krittuschi!\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne fluddinajeet to Gatta\nne teizeet to us Asklona Gelahm\nka to Wilisternu Meitas ne pre-\nzajahs/ ka to Neapgraisitu Me-\ntas ne lihgſinojahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juhs Kalni Gilboa/ la\nus juws wairs ne irr Raffaned\nLeetus/ nedg Tihrumu/ no t\nPazelfchanas Uppuri nahk/\ntur irr to Warrenu preekfchtu-\nranas BrunnasSmeekla liktas\ntahs preekſchturamas Bruzza\nSaula/ ittin ka buhtu tas ar E-\nne fwaidihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jonatana Stohps ne ka\nirr atpakat dsihfs/ un Sau-\nSohbins ne kad irr tukſch atgre-\nsees no to Nokantu Affinim/\nno to Warrenu Taukeem,\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
